Description


Show me more
WEATHER for Android. 
Weather forecast for all the world, satellite, wind & sea, surf, webcams, real time weather, widgets, geolocation. A great app with more than 10.000.000 downloads!


NOTES:
- widgets aren't available if you install or move this app to SD card;
- on multiuser devices, it works only with the default user;
- to remove a city from Favorites, long press on it and choose "Remove" from popup menu;
- if you have problems, try first to uninstall and reinstall, then contact us by mail, thanks.







